{"tid":1632450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【心痛手足】我地要行落去，就唔可以俾恐懼支配。","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:37:42.000Z","uid":84756,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e79c2bc510027543ac77d548368c9dffa10236aa","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:56.000Z","msg":"利申 和理非地區twitter文宣組 遊行例牌會出<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月行動<br />\n我發現手足對周圍人事反應都敏感咗好多<br />\n之前有藍絲黎挑釁大家都係識影相多謝 但呢排好似總會有人忍唔住打咗先算<br />\n我明白係前線保持警覺好重要<br />\n但由此睇得出大家嘅恐懼感越黎越重<br />\n<br />\n可能係因為身邊戰友拉下一個又一個<br />\n可能係因為驚淺黃會慢慢失去反抗意志<br />\n可能係因為政府出招越黎越辣但我方又動唔到佢分毫<br />\n但懇請大家記返清 呢個本來就係大衛同歌利亞之戰<br />\n我地要贏 係要靠創意靠智慧靠團結靠命硬 和勇缺一我地都係必敗<br />\n<br />\n我地要對政權持續施壓 但唔可以操之過急<br />\n不斷裝修冇錯係可以嚇怕班黑紅藍 但同時亦會影響國際對香港人的觀感(不論外國質疑係咪合理)<br />\n要記住我地終極目標係令香港人有自治權並能夠獨立地係國際立足<br />\n而要達成呢個理想 係要有好多好多嘅準備 單單同民主國家解釋裝修私了都夠大工程啦<br />\n再加上 民族建構 政治論述 外交人才 武裝力量 全部都冇可能係短時間做到<br />\n<br />\n講咁多廢話唔係想同各位手足講要和理非回合乜乜柒柒<br />\n講好咗不割 大家做咩我地文宣組都全力支援<br />\n但我只係希望大家唔好逼得自己咁緊 每次行動都係知道自己想點而唔係俾恐懼支配<br />\n我地要贏嘅係戰爭 唔好太執著於每一場小戰役的得失<br />\n攰嘅話不妨轉下職睇下書同其他人傾下計 除咗上前線都有好多野幫到香港嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人，反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa97e28b6e3cbec3b6d6f10676b2e483568e0a77","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:05:45.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n每次見到咁細個都好心痛"},{"pid":"da709160fb2ba089bc577fc4bfd462f1736bf806","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n香港人團結唔認輸就唔會輸"},{"pid":"262e43725b4055c491694076c2bcb2d805c03abe","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n多謝前線付出"},{"pid":"f8c852ac4f80bb365a861c37789709b65c7fa590","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n我地啲老野冇鬼用"},{"pid":"fc4667dd4c26e1eac6f4ece8b0d77c051f992dba","tid":1632450,"uid":204504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eae3fa1b7eeef10f8b398a778a9567499b9a782","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"5<br />\n大家要撐住，黎明始終會來臨"},{"pid":"f1ab23c18024388b5d562028fccee1b4f86f1e02","tid":1632450,"uid":204504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:09:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eacbd2b5b78a47a2800eb4f1269bc20c3b685079","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"6<br />\n去個旅行都好，抽離下唔洗日日都咁緊張"},{"pid":"74d9cec4442765eec52f756b0c5fbc4d500f07af","tid":1632450,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">今晚既連登超多兩極分化, 充滿負能量, 玩住TWITTER先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【3分鐘懶人包】依家整埋bot 教你玩 twitter, 連翻譯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594532\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594532</a><br />\n<br />\n進階<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b6427f6d90eb25cfd18baf5af7a10c0de4b099d9","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"7<br />\n由極速四大分類已經睇到我地可以進化得好快"},{"pid":"518cbf763a3c11c2239524c2ce866d275594e20d","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"8<br />\n不分化不割蓆"},{"pid":"6fc4a563a3ba4838363492de1373ae094080afb6","tid":1632450,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"932f29cd4b3705e640e9f8f22abad836c1f05698","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"9<br />\n香港人，齊上齊落"},{"pid":"ef41ffa77fd07761313ec3435dea2706118e6789","tid":1632450,"uid":33759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d68cac75d991104c7b600c9015bfd94b6cc279b","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"10<br />\n老實講，如果集香港人的力量都係唔夠打嘅話，我都會覺得係一場勝利。寧鳴而死，不默而生。但最唔想見到係因為環境壓力令香港人發揮唔到最大潛能。"},{"pid":"b351b6eeb99beb2716678b0a531a2d0a3a70f23d","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:16:15.000Z","msg":"推郁佢可以嗎"},{"pid":"59ae59df352a698742b7850d90993075e47aa988","tid":1632450,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c7e2b32d77d1aa1a7d7c0439e88330adeb442b1","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:17:17.000Z","msg":"連登第一個大型「樹洞」上線了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632082</a>"},{"pid":"5920612cbf3beb2d9c491ef86966998c21f341d3","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d188dfac1ac79c00c1e74083549881a53da52daa","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0196ec7e546010e11019a65bc0d0dde5d842e686","tid":1632450,"uid":84756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"